textBox.richText: My name is D'Ann one of the first people that will greet you when you walk into the orthodontic clinic.  It is my pleasure and a privilege to work at such a world renowned institution such as UCSF. I come to UCSF with 18 years of dental experience, as a registered dental assistant and dental assisting instructor. As the front desk treatment coordinator, I will provide you and your family with a hassle free orthodontic experience. In my spare time I enjoy the outdoors, cooking new recipes, reading and watching girls’ basketball.  My favorite quote: Smiles are Contagious
